Dear colleagues,
I want to start by expressing my heartfelt gratitude to everyone contributi=
ng to the successful launch of the Up Our Game Canada! program on Friday, F=
ebruary 21. Your efforts are making this initiative a reality, and I truly =
appreciate your dedication.
Here=92s a quick update on our progress and the amazing people who are doin=
g the work:

  *   Leadership: Ensure that successful implementation of the program earn=
s Sprott a leadership position across Canada, from coast to coast to coast.=
 (Howard)
  *   Registrations: We have 45 registrants, though our room capacity is 28=
. (Dan)
  *   Website launch: The program website will go live on Wednesday, Februa=
ry 19. (Dan, Kim & Elizabeth)
  *   Content development: Content for seven modules has been developed. (I=
an & Eduardo)
  *
Video and podcast production: Six of seven videos (with transcripts) and po=
dcasts are ready. (Enoh)
  *
Workshop: Workshop structure and instructions are being developed and will =
be implemented on Feb 21. (Eduardo)
  *   Corpus: A curated corpus has been uploaded into three AI spaces that =
program participants can access via Perplexity, ChatGPT, or NotebookLLM (En=
oh & Joe)
  *
Media & outreach: Articles and promotional content are being developed and =
will be disseminated early next week. (Emma, Kim, Steven, & Dan)
  *
Support services: Service offers to support marketing, payments, infrastruc=
ture, contracts, and compliance are being developed. (Calvin, Jaclyn, Mawue=
na & Shona)
  *
Content & teaching offers, introductions: Offers have been received to deve=
lop content, teach, or facilitate introductions. (Fran=E7ois, John, Linda D=
., Rebecca)
  *   Research initiatives: TIM students are formulating research projects =
to help advance the program. (Anni, Breck, Zeyi)
  *   Country links: Developing country specific links (Jerry, Troy)
  *   Potential partners contacted: uOttawa and Ottawa Board of Trade (Edua=
rdo)

It=92s been an absolute pleasure working with each of you!
Time is tight, but I feel we are in good shape for the launch, and I couldn=
=92t be more excited about what we=92ve accomplished together. Thank you al=
l for your contributions!
Looking forward to Friday Feb 21!
Tony B.



--_000_YT1PR01MB4455170727C1BE2DA4EED1A69BFF2YT1PR01MB4455CANP_
